        "summary": "Minister of State for Railways Ravneet Singh Bittu has said that Prime Minister Narendra Modi will inaugurate the redeveloped Jalandhar Cantonment Railway Station and other developmental projects in Punjab this month. He said around 75 completed Amrit Bharat Stations will be virtually inaugurated by the Prime Minister from Jalandhar Cantt station. Speaking to the media […]",
