        "summary": "In the forex market today, the rupee appreciated by 44 paise to close at 94 rupees and 96 paise against the US dollar. The dollar index, which indicates the US dollar&#8217;s strength against a basket of six other leading currencies, was trading at 100.87 in intra-day trade today.",
